relevant_findings.HEENT: Sclera anicteric, dry mucous membranes, oropharynx clear
relevant_findings.neck: Supple, JVP not elevated, no lymphadenopathy
relevant_findings.lungs: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, rhonchi
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, normal S1 + S2, no murmurs, rubs, gallops
relevant_findings.abdomen: Soft, bowel sounds present, no rebound tenderness or guarding, no organomegaly, no stigmata of liver disease
relevant_findings.extremities: Warm, well perfused, 2+ pulses, no clubbing, cyanosis or edema
